= Dadka ay dhalyo la tahay beesha Reer Xaamid =
Reer Xaamid waxa ay dhalyo la tahay beelaha kale ee reer bicidyahan sida reer wacays, reer Maxamed Gaala eri, reer Samatar, reer Maxamed Gaala eri, Bah-wagardhac, reer Sugul, Maxamuud Yoonis, Ismaaciil Yoonis iyo kuwa kale.

= Deegaanada ay degaan Reer Xaamid =
